{"tid":1781113,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"做黑警衰撚過新移民呃福利 希望政府下調黑警薪金及福利","createTime":"2019-12-13T02:21:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-13T06:21:10.000Z","uid":336524,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3d0f70a6e6a6c1e4346afe63e8eac988b175b24c","tid":1781113,"uid":336524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T02:21:14.000Z","msg":"中六畢業 有手有腳就24000起薪 加一堆福利<br />\n<br />\n講學歷係垃圾。<br />\n講體能又係廢，唔攞消防員做比較，輸九條街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n攞地盤、拆櫃苦力比都比唔上。人地係咁拆野搬野，仲好力過黑警。同普通做開運動嘅學生哥無分別。<br />\n消防員就話出入火場下水道危險啫，黑警鬼死咁安全，見人埋身就開槍殺人。分分鐘坐係電腦枱到做mon po狗咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n專業知識又無，從來無見過黑警做急救。成日拖行啲打暈左嘅人同中槍嘅人。<br />\n<br />\n黑警做埋晒啲傷天害理嘅野仲有一堆福利，衰撚過啲呃綜援嘅人，起碼人地無害人。"},{"pid":"7d12a7ec5fbf9246a4d671da1fd8196a9cde6ee5","tid":1781113,"uid":336524,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T02:23:00.000Z","msg":"幾撚時減佢地人工啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然有排未睇到美國制裁佢地<br />\n減人工得喇掛<br />\n快啲減鳩佢地人工<br />\n今年香港出現財赤，佢地係時候減人工共渡難關"},{"pid":"53345202cf6a5144d57182343c4ed0c7878bd686","tid":1781113,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T02:23:09.000Z","msg":"就咁睇唔會"},{"pid":"ce81df57c94966fd99e8af08ff1223ca6d733c1f","tid":1781113,"uid":57674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T02:23:18.000Z","msg":"本來高薪係諗住養廉<br />\n點知今時今日<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5bb0b70932c1d3eb4328b64479b0d6f7c8e8417","tid":1781113,"uid":336524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T02:24:23.000Z","msg":"好撚辛苦咩差佬ot?<br />\n我地工人有時趕住起場都連續做2、3日啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地憑咩咁高人工"},{"pid":"53020f1cde4df9e7743aa9e8a13ba6ed8a7f8026","tid":1781113,"uid":336524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T02:26:02.000Z","msg":"希望大家標簽佢地做社會寄生蟲 地底泥<br />\n賤過呃福利嘅新移民"},{"pid":"4e5fe6b1662ae9518c5e0529de2b47a3b04f13c5","tid":1781113,"uid":336524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce81df57c94966fd99e8af08ff1223ca6d733c1f","tid":1781113,"uid":57674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T02:23:18.000Z","msg":"本來高薪係諗住養廉<br />\n點知今時今日<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T02:27:07.000Z","msg":"養左班曱甴出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99ff2abb8f79a0206a927756e27470c6636c15ab","tid":1781113,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T02:39:06.000Z","msg":"減一半Ok?"},{"pid":"35c786ac9799a81b6ca80bd02ff826cd975c7dbc","tid":1781113,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99ff2abb8f79a0206a927756e27470c6636c15ab","tid":1781113,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T02:39:06.000Z","msg":"減一半Ok?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T02:57:35.000Z","msg":"最低工資啦"},{"pid":"3ca2ea03f584568ccc65e9e8cc988755ce8edf78","tid":1781113,"uid":336524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T03:13:00.000Z","msg":"希望可以標簽黑警做蠶食社會資優嘅垃圾<br />\n唔止係殺人犯強姦犯仲係寄生蟲"},{"pid":"96a7e256ca54826d8b77d6c2e7de3c2b784c3e0c","tid":1781113,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35c786ac9799a81b6ca80bd02ff826cd975c7dbc","tid":1781113,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99ff2abb8f79a0206a927756e27470c6636c15ab","tid":1781113,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T02:39:06.000Z","msg":"減一半Ok?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T02:57:35.000Z","msg":"最低工資啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T06:21:10.000Z","msg":"等佢地知道點樣憑良心做事先考慮加番人工"}]}